<body>
<div1 type="summary">
<p>Preparation to go to New Orleans</p>
</div1>

<div1 type="body">

<p><date_mentioned n="12-04-1835">Decr 4 1835</date_mentioned></p>

<p>Dr <person_mentioned>brother</person_mentioned>; I think shall leave <date_mentioned n="12-08-1835">in four days</date_mentioned> for your <location_mentioned>house </location_mentioned>my health
is not good—shall start to <location_mentioned>Orleans </location_mentioned>as soon as possible—Enquire so as to
let me know when and what kind of vessell there is</p>

<p><person_mentioned>S. F. Austin</person_mentioned>—</p>

<p>[Addressed:] <person_mentioned>J. F. Perry</person_mentioned> <location_mentioned>Peach point</location_mentioned></p>


</div1>
